title: 2006 Honda Motorcycle Previews
description:
All footage is from the Paris and Tokyo Motor Shows earlier this year.  Here are the details:

Files Size:  247MB
Time:  13 min
File Format: Xvid

Bikes included:

CBR1000RR (Motor Show commercial for the RR starts before a red and black model is shown, then a Silver, then black)
Goldwing (Gold model followed by the airbag model)
CBF1000 (Black with a model on top)
CBR1000XX (Silver/grey)
CBF600 (Black)
DN-01 (Unveiling show)
E4-01
CBR1000RR (Red)
CBR600RR (Telefonica Special Edition)
After these bikes are a small sample of the upcoming segments for Suzuki, Yamaha, and Kawasaki.  It features a quick peek at the Suzuki Stratosphere, Yamaha FJR, and Kawi ZZR1400
